<li>Mason, David L. <i>From Buildings and Loans to Bail-Outs: A History of the American Savings and Loan Industry, 1831–1995</i> (Cambridge University Press, 2004).</li>
<li>Meltzer, Allan H. <i>A History of the Federal Reserve</i> (2 vol. U of Chicago Press, 2010).</li>
<li>Murphy, Sharon Ann. <i>Other People's Money: How Banking Worked in the Early American Republic</i> (2017) <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://eh.net/?s=+Murphy%2C+Sharon+Ann">online review</a></li>
<li>Pak, Susie J. <i>Gentlemen Bankers. The World of J.P. Morgan</i> (2013) 1880s-1910</li>
